      • create

        public static OMSQueryCondition create(java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> condition)
        Static method to create a new query condition object from a parsed map entry. If the condition applies to the OMM id, an OMSQueryIDContition will be created, otherwise an OMSQueryAttributeCondition.
        Parameters:
        condition - The search condition as a map Entry<String, Object>.
        Returns:
        An OMSQueryCondition if its creation was successful, otherwise null.
